            "author_text": "<p>Honestly wasn’t sure what to expect, but it’s actually really cute. The fit is decent and the details look nice in person. It’s a bit delicate though so you have to be careful.</p>",
            "select_product": "here-s-an-etsy-seo-optimized-title-70-characters-and-description-for-your-dress",
